ZH: 你弟弟时不时会发点脾气。
EN: Your younger brother gets angry from time to time.

ZH: 她时不时会打个电话给我。
EN: She calls me occasionally.

ZH: 他时不时会搂着我走在街上。
EN: He walks with his arm around me from time to time.

ZH: 时不时我会在公园里运动一下。
EN: Occasionally, I exercise in the park.

ZH: 她时不时会提醒我戴口罩。
EN: She reminds me to wear a mask every now and then.

ZH: 在中国的大城市，时不时就有交通堵塞的情况。
EN: In major cities in China, traffic congestion occurs from time to time.

ZH: 我们时不时会组织一次团建活动。
EN: We organize team-building activities occasionally.

ZH: 他时不时和同事开个小玩笑。
EN: He occasionally jokes around with his colleagues.

ZH: 我时不时会给家人写一封信。
EN: I write a letter to my family every now and then.

ZH: 每个月，我们时不时会去看一场电影。
EN: Every month, we go to see a movie from time to time.

ZH: 假期时不时抽出时间去旅行是件愉快的事情。
EN: It is enjoyable to take some time off during holidays and travel occasionally.

ZH: 我时不时会看看电视剧来放松自己。
EN: Occasionally, I watch TV dramas to relax.

ZH: 他喜欢时不时挑战一些新的饮食。
EN: He likes to occasionally try new diets.

ZH: 我们时不时会一起去咖啡馆喝杯咖啡。
EN: We occasionally go to a café together for a cup of coffee.

ZH: 看到漂亮的花朵时不时会让人心情愉悦。
EN: Seeing beautiful flowers occasionally brightens one's mood.

ZH: 她时不时给我发一些有趣的短信。
EN: She occasionally sends me funny text messages.

ZH: 我们时不时会在周末做一次家庭聚餐。
EN: We occasionally have a family dinner on weekends.

ZH: 夏天的时候，我们时不时去海滩放松一下。
EN: During summer, we occasionally go to the beach to relax.

ZH: 时不时出去吃一顿，在家煮饭实在是太累了。
EN: Going out for a meal occasionally is much easier than cooking at home.

ZH: 这家餐厅的服务员时不时提醒客人录下美食。
EN: The restaurant's waitstaff occasionally remind customers to take pictures of their delicious dishes.

ZH: 他时不时冒出一些有趣的主意。
EN: He occasionally comes up with some interesting ideas.
